column2: SELECT TOP #  p.htmID,  p.objid,  p.ra,  p.dec,  p.u,  p.g,  p.r,  p.i,  p.z,  p.run,  p.rerun,  p.camcol,  p.field,  p.clean,  s.specobjid,  s.class,  s.z as redshift,  s.plate,  s.mjd,  s.fiberid FROM  PhotoObj AS p JOIN SpecObj AS s  ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE  p.clean = #  AND  p.u BETWEEN # AND #  AND  p.g BETWEEN # AND #  AND  (p.htmID * # & #) < (# * #)
